Troubleshooting
Common Issues
Issue: Version bump doesn't work

Verify VERSION file exists and is readable
Check file permissions: chmod 644 VERSION
Ensure version format is correct (MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH)
Issue: Build script fails

Check if all source files exist in src/ directory
Verify tar command is available: which tar
Ensure build and metadata directories are writable
Issue: Git tag creation fails

Verify Git repository is initialized: git status
Check if tag already exists: git tag -l
Ensure you have committed changes before tagging
Issue: Metadata JSON is invalid

Validate with: jq empty metadata/*.json
Check for special characters in variables
Verify jq is installed: which jq
Issue: Checksum verification fails

Ensure artifact hasn't been modified after build
Check metadata file corresponds to correct artifact
Verify sha256sum command is available
